lead_paragraph: THE MINOT'S ROCK LIGHT.--The Boston Journal of Saturday has the following item: "We learn that Capt. Bennett has resigned his situaation as keeper of Minot's Rock Light Ship. The principal reason which has induced him to take this step is the insecurity of the light-ship.
